			<title>Podcast beta 3, released</title>
			<link>http://jlleblanc.com/articles/34-podcast-beta-3-released</link>
			<guid>http://jlleblanc.com/articles/34-podcast-beta-3-released</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[
The Podcast suite, beta 3, is now released. Download the <a href="http://jlleblanc.com/bot_podcast_b3.zip">mambot</a>, <a href="http://jlleblanc.com/mod_podcast_b3.zip">module</a>, and <a href="http://jlleblanc.com/com_podcast_b3.zip">component</a> (only the component has changed, so you can skip downloading the other two if all you want to do is switch out the old component for the new). iTunes support has been added, but due to the nature of Apple's listing policies, this functionality has not been tested. UTF-8 is now the default encoding (which is preferred by Apple).<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Update:</span> Small patch made to the <a href="http://jlleblanc.com/com_podcast_b3.zip">component</a> to eliminate repeating iTunes image tag. (<span style="font-style: italic;">September 19th, 2005</span>)<br />
]]></description>
